Corinna Harney https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Corinna_Harney 0 Corinna Harney (born February 20, 1972) is an American model and actress. She was chosen as Playboy's Playmate of the Month for August 1991 and Playboy's Playmate of the Year for 1992. At age 20, she became the youngest Playmate of the Year ever at that point. Harney is sometimes credited as Corina Harney, Corinna Harney-Jones, or Corinna Harney Jones. Corinna_Harney ( born February_20_,_1972 ) is an_American_model_and_actress .
